@startuml WandbConfig
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

title WandbConfig Class Diagram

class WandbConfig {
  + enabled: bool = True
  + project: str = "entropy seesaw"
  + run_name: str = "TreePO_experiment"
  + entity: Optional[str] = None
  + tags: List[str]
  + extras: Dict[str, Any]
  --
  + __init__()
}

class WandbLogger {
  + _wandb: Module
  + _cfg: WandbConfig
  + _run: Run
  --
  + init(context)
  + log(metrics)
  + close()
}

WandbConfig ..> WandbLogger : used by

note right of WandbConfig
  Configuration for Weights & Biases logging:
  - Enable/disable logging
  - Project and run naming
  - Entity (team/organization)
  - Tags for run organization
  - Additional configuration
end note

@enduml

